'''Vratix''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Vratix/Legends|Vratix]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Thyferra/Legends|Thyferra]]. It was high-pitched and used clicking sounds and even skin [[Color/Legends|color]] changes for punctuation. Species and [[Droid/Legends|droids]] physically unable to change color and click could understand Vratix language, but not speak it. However, the Vratix were a social species, trading with many other races. Thus, most Vratix were fluent in both Vratix and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]], being literate in both languages.

